%h1 Listing Coupon Codes

%p Coupon codes can be created in order to provide a discount (or even FREE) on certain items.

%table
  %tr
    %th Name
    %th Code
    %th Description
    %th Price
    %th Expense Items
    %th
  - @coupon_codes.each do |coupon_code|
    %tr
      %td= link_to coupon_code.name, coupon_code_summary_path(coupon_code)
      %td= coupon_code.code
      %td= coupon_code.description
      %td= coupon_code.price
      %td= coupon_code.coupon_code_expense_items.map(&:expense_item).map(&:to_s).join(", ")
      %td= link_to 'Edit', edit_coupon_code_path(coupon_code)
      %td= link_to 'Delete', coupon_code, method: :delete, data: { confirm: 'Are you sure?' }
%br

%fieldset.form__fieldset
  %h3 New Coupon Code
  = render 'form'
